{"tid":1221112,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢到係地鐵，每人一句「香港加油」","createTime":"2019-06-14T06:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:43:53.000Z","uid":167992,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fbeb86031315b77c8ea678d47f10a8d16ff7ae","tid":1221112,"uid":167992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到，每一卡地鐵入面，一落車就聽到有人大嗌一句「香港加油」。<br />\n車入面個個都響應返一句「香港加油」。<br />\n四個字雖然唔可以幫助到啲咩，但四個字亦都唔難講出口，又唔使成本。<br />\n希望可以喚醒返香港人，唔好再冷眼旁觀。<br />\nNoise 由基本做起<br />\n星期日６月１６日見，我會夜啲到。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64318420_453971102054413_4022480723767197696_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=fe65e717d01e01fc1de2af03a14d2d97&amp;oe=5D8AB405\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64318420_453971102054413_4022480723767197696_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Dfe65e717d01e01fc1de2af03a14d2d97%26oe%3D5D8AB405&h=123a9ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit: 台灣極地攝影師「馬賽Kyo」</div>"},{"pid":"8723bf58af7370183bee263e45984e4759d94cc9","tid":1221112,"uid":167992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}